Class Dot2TreeNodes

  • java.lang.Object
    • models.Dot2TreeNodes
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Dot2TreeInnerNode, Dot2TreeLeafNode

    public class Dot2TreeNodes
extends Object
    Helper class which stores information for each individual (leaf/inner) node. Including linkage to other inner/leaf nodes and suffix link information.
    Author:
    Christopher Kraus
